      • getRcp

        public static byte[] getRcp(boolean statusCheck,
                            boolean zeroCheck,
                            boolean option,
                            boolean transactionLimitActive,
                            boolean floorLimitActive,
                            boolean cmvLimitActive)
        Reader configuration parameters.
        Parameters:
        statusCheck - Status Check. true - Enable, false - Disable.
        zeroCheck - Amount, authorized of Zero Check. true - Enable, false - Disable.
        option - Amount, authorized of Zero Option. true - Option1, false - Option2. This is only applicable when the reader is online-capable.
        transactionLimitActive - Contactless transaction limit check. true - Enable, false - Disable.
        floorLimitActive - Contactless floor limit check. true - Enable, false - Disable.
        cmvLimitActive - CVM required limit check. true - Enable, false - Disable.
        Returns:
